THE N1 South at the John Vorster exit in
Centurion was closed off to traffic, due to a truck that is on fire on Thursday afternoon.
Traffic officials advised motorisists to use alternative routes
as all lanes were closed at the Rigel Avenue.Motorists were advised to get off at the Botha Avenue and
